{"tid":259950,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"香港個國際車展真係垃撚圾","createTime":"2017-05-27T10:51:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-28T10:04:51.000Z","uid":107582,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c0baa4417bb1ea50d716a39f80dcb1114c898f06","tid":259950,"uid":107582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T10:51:21.000Z","msg":"同外國個啲真係冇得比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n澳門台灣都搞得好睇過香港<br />\n得LOTUS廠放左9部出黎叫做好好睇睇<br />\n不過啲古董車係幾罕有 <br />\n啲racing simulator排左好耐隊都味玩到<br />\n放啲大陸車 拖頭喺到都唔知做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nAuto Show facebook page仲話有價值2000萬既mclaren p1 去到又見唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 模型車就大撚把<br />\n不過點都希望香港整多啲汽車活動車展車聚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5579d421c9b916920e9c3f06adcbc02cbcf8fa70","tid":259950,"uid":665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T11:16:09.000Z","msg":"有免費飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過冇去到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d33b89d9f2d8b651790d44bf94d067ff88e1ad9","tid":259950,"uid":54655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T11:23:17.000Z","msg":"特登上黎睇下有無Review<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0f05f4fbfb63ee4d042493e4849939fe8cdf1ac","tid":259950,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T12:19:23.000Z","msg":"上海車展仲勁"},{"pid":"86ced196eed72b0bab9f72bded9b8d141f50d70f","tid":259950,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T12:21:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"768a12ca3baa02625a2614fe515d58d7526d262f","tid":259950,"uid":38946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T12:36:14.000Z","msg":"慳番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac2eef82ebb9579b5d2d594e745c4a1074e76cfc","tid":259950,"uid":33961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T14:42:00.000Z","msg":"屌你老母個車展真係伏到仆街<br />\n仲要比佢呃鳩左50 蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成個場有 1/3 既位劃左黎比強國車<br />\nD 強國車仲要樣衰到嘔 連間廠都未撚聽過<br />\n都算啦 連田螺車都放埋出黎把撚咩我屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外大牛 馬莎個區又係唔知做乜<br />\n圍封哂都算 仲要架架都屎忽向出<br />\n我想睇下個頭要企到九萬幾里遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過lotus 同古董車個區係唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連e type 都班到返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"205432624feaf8a53acf8886062d0d087fe80ff8","tid":259950,"uid":107582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T16:11:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母個車展真係伏到仆街<br />\n仲要比佢呃鳩左50 蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成個場有 1/3 既位劃左黎比強國車<br />\nD 強國車仲要樣衰到嘔 連間廠都未撚聽過<br />\n都算啦 連田螺車都放埋出黎把撚咩我屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外大牛 馬莎個區又係唔知做乜<br />\n圍封哂都算 仲要架架都屎忽向出<br />\n我想睇下個頭要企到九萬幾里遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過lotus 同古董車個區係唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連e type 都班到返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAgree<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nD強國車狗也不屌 <br />\n不過有得試坐38噸貨車 拖頭又幾難得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nLotus有部落場車可以坐上去又幾驚喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n古董車大部分都見過哂 最靚係e type 同部911 3.8RS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會展隔離一號車場仲多靚車睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有佢個停車場啲車仲罕 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aa3452c9ef670578b14054823ce1c84d460c90d","tid":259950,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T16:20:48.000Z","msg":"有Citroen DS同2cv，仲有福特Model A，Fiat X19同馬莎，都係好難見到<br />\n除左水上電單車，仲有潛水器同水上飄賣，成十幾廿萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n假日就預左打機要排餐死<br />\n之前中環海旁同屯門既車展都好正"},{"pid":"a95fe45382fa36d582afdd7876586df0f3b621fd","tid":259950,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T16:22:03.000Z","msg":"Mx5全家福都唔錯，爭部RF"},{"pid":"34818125c54d5c819e28d3a3783dc5a91ae84835","tid":259950,"uid":107582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T18:12:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有Citroen DS同2cv，仲有福特Model A，Fiat X19同馬莎，都係好難見到<br />\n除左水上電單車，仲有潛水器同水上飄賣，成十幾廿萬<img src=\"/assets/fa